 ogs\u00e5 en plikt n\u00e5r \u00abOmstendighetene krever at det gripes inn uten opphold for \u00e5 verne liv, helse eller vesentlige samfunnsverdier\u00bb, opplyser politiet i pressemeldinga."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1fc0e2001693d89db0764d79b8dd7c1aad12e2afe30deee186286755100f7313"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T01:58:18.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Polititjenestemannen p\u00e5 frivakt var i sin fulle rett til \u00e5 frata den unge mannen p\u00e5 H\u00f8ylandet f\u00f8rerkortet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10829876.ece/f3f0ab/ALTERNATES/w980-default/07NYHtrafikksak2.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f550981eb48b7a616fbfb4791590f4fef79bf182.jpg?59439b5a"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Politimann p\u00e5 frivakt hadde lov til \u00e5 frata sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren f\u00f8rerkort -adressa.no", "Ikke uvanlig", "Vurdering"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "f550981eb48b7a616fbfb4791590f4fef79bf182"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["frata", "vurderes", "politimann", "frata sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren", "frivakt", "f\u00f8rerkort", "gripe", "plikt", "sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren f\u00f8rerkort", "politi", "opplyser politiet", "frata sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren f\u00f8rerkort"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["omstendighetene", "namdalsavisa"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value":